{
  "stem": "13584.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I was staying with my brother there in this little-- little hole with the other-- I remember-- I didn't understand why, but one evening, my brother and me-- some people used to-- came and asked us to get out.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it was a girl of the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was a mother and a girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The girl was maybe-- I don't know-- 13, 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And apparently she was raped there, and they were taking away to a hospital, or that's what I remember.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then the mother and-- mother and daughter moved out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were staying there in this hole, you know, in the-- and I remember one day a Kazakh approached my mother, and he wanted to buy my brother.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He was small.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was then two years old, two and a half years old, with curly blond hair.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he wanted to buy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he insisted he wanted to buy his boy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He had to buy this boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Of course, my mother didn't-- didn't sell, didn't go for it-- for some wheat or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "From there, we moved-- and I don't know what was the reasons we moved-- to a place-- used to in Russian call it stancja, which is probably a settlement-- called Chiili, also in Kazakhstan, not far from the city Kizilordu.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Over there, we had a horrible time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I remember my mother, as a wife of a soldier-- and then we stopped knowing anything about my father.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We did not-- where he is, what's happened to him, in which parts, if he's alive or not.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We did not know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's even before that-- before, a few months after-- after we moved from-- from the-- from the village, from the kolkhoz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The knowledge about him was interrupted.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
